data.name: RichTextBox1.Text
data.value: Your computer has been locked for downloading illegal material. The only way to unlock it is to complete a survey. If you don't complete the survey before the timer runs out (Approx 2hrs), all your files will be deleted and your hard-drive corrupt. step 1) Click survey, complete a survey. step 2) Once you have completed it correctly, a text-file will download with a password in it. step 3) Enter the password in the text-box and click 'Unlock', your computer will then be restored back to normal.
